#{{italbrac|biochemistry}} A [[steroid]] [[hormone]], produced by the [[adrenal cortex]], that [[regulate]]s the [[metabolism]] of [[carbohydrate]]s and maintains [[blood pressure]].
#{{italbrac|medicine}} a [[synthetic]] version of this hormone used to treat [[Addison's disease]] and other conditions.
